[Groans]

347
00:28:16,761 --> 00:28:19,491
[Gasping]

348
00:28:26,905 --> 00:28:28,839
<i>- [Knocking]
- [Seiko] Hello.</i>

349
00:28:28,907 --> 00:28:33,139
Hey.
