350
00:28:33,211 --> 00:28:35,907
- Is everything okay?
- Uh-

351
00:28:38,416 --> 00:28:40,646
Uh, yeah.

352
00:28:42,454 --> 00:28:45,048
Uh, yeah, yeah, yeah.
Everything's fine. I just- I, um-

