555
00:50:38,869 --> 00:50:42,305
<i>She wouldn't leave me alone.</i>

556
00:50:42,372 --> 00:50:45,239
<i>She followed me everywhere.</i>

557
00:50:45,309 --> 00:50:48,710
<i>- Bruno and Adam said they'd talk to her.
- And?</i>

558
00:50:48,779 --> 00:50:54,274
