594
00:52:46,430 --> 00:52:48,364
If I'd have known
this was necessary...

595
00:52:48,432 --> 00:52:50,457
I would've worn something
a little nicer.

596
00:52:52,602 --> 00:52:55,400
That's gonna be just fine.

597
00:53:05,549 --> 00:53:07,779
I'm a little bit nervous.

598
00:53:07,851 --> 00:53:10,786
