612
00:54:42,479 --> 00:54:45,539
It's Bruno.

613
00:54:45,615 --> 00:54:49,244
- Hey, man. Uh-
- There's been an accident.

614
00:54:49,319 --> 00:54:52,550
- It's, uh, Adam.
