650
00:59:08,278 --> 00:59:10,212
<i>We're not going anywhere.</i>

651
00:59:25,161 --> 00:59:27,959
These pictures were taken
before the crash.

652
00:59:28,031 --> 00:59:31,626
- How can she possibly-
